```
2. Create an interface that defines the methods you want to intercept:
```csharp
public interface IMyInterface
{
    void MyMethod();
}
```
3. Create a class that implements the `IInterceptor` interface to define the behavior of the interceptor:
```csharp
public class MyInterceptor : IInterceptor
{
    public void Intercept(IInvocation invocation)
    {
        Console.WriteLine("Before method call");
        invocation.Proceed();
        Console.WriteLine("After method call");
    }
}
```
