```csharp
proxy.MyMethod();
```
This will output:
```
Before method call
After method call
```
The `CreateInterfaceProxyWithTarget` method creates a dynamic proxy that implements the specified interface and forwards method calls to the specified target object. The `MyInterceptor` class is used to intercept method calls and add additional behavior before and after the method call.

